WEBVTT

10:15.160 --> 10:16.280 line:80%
She nodded just now,

10:16.280 --> 10:18.010 line:80%
and now she's shaking her head.

10:18.800 --> 10:20.530 line:80%
Fan Changning, I'm asking you.

10:20.550 --> 10:21.640 line:80%
Don't lie.

10:21.640 --> 10:22.710 line:80%
Lying will make your mouth rot.

10:22.710 --> 10:23.040 line:80%
You know that?

10:23.040 --> 10:23.670 line:80%
Get away!
